FTwitterHelpBot&d=Wg3pkMW64ksxbb%2FAt9Sry7Xqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=4fd2675b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">入<span style=\"color: violet;\"> /task1</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZWmYt8Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZWmYt8Z.png&h=b245ba88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\ntask1所顯示的25條tweets<br />\n係嚴重唔夠人<br />\n（大佬呀條條上唔到一千點搞呀？）<br />\n<br />\n最後咪撚再串錯hongkong!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"598b13b2ff6ffd9a345ae9fd2dc5b0de533b58a2","tid":1658531,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:19:12.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}